    <item>
      <title>挪威维持利率稳定，并暗示 2025 年将首次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/norway-keeps-rate-steady-with-signal-for-first-cut-only-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威央行坚持富裕国家中最强硬的货币政策立场之一，打破了投资者对挪威央行最早在今年推进首次降低借贷成本计划的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/norway-keeps-rate-steady-with-signal-for-first-cut-only-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 08:06:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲电动汽车销量暴跌，汽车制造商寻求欧盟援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-19/europe-s-august-car-sales-fall-16-5-yoy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月份，德国电动汽车市场暴跌，导致欧洲整体汽车市场普遍下滑。欧洲汽车制造商协会敦促欧盟委员会在 2025 年实现汽车排放目标之前采取紧急救济措施。彭博社的 Oliver Crook 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-19/europe-s-august-car-sales-fall-16-5-yoy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 07:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率预期和股息推动新加坡股市升至 17 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/singapore-stocks-head-for-17-year-high-on-rate-hopes-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于降息前景提振了新加坡房地产投资信托基金，并提升了高收益市场的吸引力，新加坡股市攀升至 2007 年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/singapore-stocks-head-for-17-year-high-on-rate-hopes-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 03:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
